### 1. 用户登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. 获取用户信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 获取订单列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/order/list?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 创建新订单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/order/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trackingNo": "YT999888777",
  "expressCompany": "圆通速递",
  "pickupAddress": "学校西门快递站",
  "deliveryAddress": "5号楼301宿舍",
  "remark": "小件快递，请尽快取件",
  "fee": 3.00,
  "expectedTime": "2026-03-15 18:00:00"
}

### 5. 获取H2数据库控制台
GET http://localhost:8080/h2-console

### 6. 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### 7. 获取系统信息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/system/info